{ Play the Reti. } { [%csl Yf3][%cal Yg1f3] }
1. Nf3 c6 { Again, here's my recommendation. Play d4. } 2. d4 d5 { Develop the bishop to f4. } 3. Bf4 Nf6 { Push pawn up to e3. } 4. e3 { If Bf5 is ever played, you play c4 followed by Qb3. } 4... e6 { Develop the knight to d2. } 5. Nbd2 Nbd7 { Develop the bishop to d3. } 6. Bd3 Be7 { Castle the king. } 7. O-O O-O { Now, you can push the pawn to e4. } 8. e4 $16 { White is now better. } *


