{ [%csl Bf3][%cal Bg1f3] }
1. Nf3 f5 { Instead of playing d4, I recommend playing d3. } { [%csl Rd3][%cal Rd2d3] } 2. d3 Nf6 { We gambit the pawn again with e4! } { [%csl Ye4][%cal Ye2e4] } 3. e4! { Gambiting the pawn for initiative! } 3... fxe4 { [%csl Be4][%cal Bd3e4] } 4. dxe4 Nxe4 { Develop with tempo... } { [%csl Gd3][%cal Gf1d3] } 5. Bd3 Nf6 { Go Ng5! Setup a trap! } { [%csl Rg5][%cal Rf3g5] } 6. Ng5 $16 { It is +1.0! White is much better! Threatens Nxh7 to weaken the diagonal. } { [%csl Rh7][%cal Rg5h7] } *


