{ [%csl Bf3][%cal Bg1f3] }
1. Nf3 Nf6 { [%csl Bg3][%cal Bg2g3] } 2. g3 g6 { [%csl Bg2][%cal Bf1g2] } 3. Bg2 Bg7 { [%csl Bg1][%cal Be1g1] } 4. O-O d5 { [%csl Bd3][%cal Bd2d3] } 5. d3 O-O { [%csl Bd2][%cal Bb1d2] } 6. Nbd2 { Our main setup has been created. } { [%csl Bd3,Bd2,Bf3,Bg2,Bf2,Bg3,Bh2,Bf1,Bg1] } 6... c5 { [%csl Be4][%cal Be2e4] } 7. e4 { Our main pawn break has been achieved. } 7... Nc6 { [%csl Be1][%cal Bf1e1] } 8. Re1 e5 { [%csl Bd5][%cal Be4d5] } 9. exd5 Nxd5 { [%csl Bc4][%cal Bd2c4] } 10. Nc4 f6 { [%csl Bc3][%cal Bc2c3] } 11. c3 { Your main break is d4. } { [%csl Rd4][%cal Rd3d4] } *


